PathOfBuilding.Notes:
How to gear
When you get 1c go on trade and get embalmer and 4 link them this will last you til 2 stones+ Get 4 instilling orbs and roll res on bismith flask and this will solve most of your res problems for a long time. Pick up cheap clusters when you can and roll them When you level up more pick up a dendro when you can manage 300 dex and 150 int ( you dont have to link it or use it as your main links) Pick up Leper whenever its cheap Either pick up +1 chaos neck with dot multi or fury valve
FOR LATER When you get enough vaal orbs you want to put assassins mitts on your filter to vaal. When you start vaal them you can get temp chains for your merc and then pick up windscreams or doedres daming ring for him so he can apply temp chains for you Keep vaaling til +1 frenzy and eventually you will mythic orb them into snakebites when you switch to ralakesh setup. Put sentinel jacket on your filter and vaal them for proj gems or aoe gems and then mythic orb them for dendro (50%)
